<plot>In a Mexican Village so isolated that it still believes in magic, El Jefe rules his people with an iron fist and his family with a heavy hand. When his son, Miguel, steals a family heirloom, a series of events are put into place - with a revolutionary young Captain arriving and threatening the Mayor's power. With the help of his only friend, an old clock maker that the townspeople call Father Time, Miguel realizes that somethings can be fixed by not all people can. And it us up to him to stop his families legacy of tyrannical rule.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?190811</url></doc>
